OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783682373
OL,3,CManchester United confirm more details
OL,4,Cabout 100,000 seater stadium
OL,6,FManchester United and the local
OL,7,Fauthorities have released a video
OL,8,Fdetailing the plans for the new
OL,9,Fstadium and Stadium District.
OL,11,FUnited's new home will be based
OL,12,Fapproximately 350 metres north-west of
OL,13,Fthe existing Old Trafford stadium.
OL,15,FThe area is being described as the
OL,16,FStadium District, which will be built
OL,17,Ffor sport, entertainment and year-
OL,18,Fround activity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
