OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783682373
OL,3,CManchester United confirm more details
OL,4,Cabout 100,000 seater stadium
OL,6,FIt is said to be the "flagship
OL,7,Flandmark" of the wider Trafford
OL,8,FWharfside development.
OL,10,FThe club says it is working to
OL,11,Fbuilding a "world-class stadium" with
OL,12,Fsupporters at the forefront of
OL,13,Fdecision-making.
OL,15,FCollette Roche, CEO, New Stadium
OL,16,FDevelopment at Manchester United, said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
