FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783682373
OL,3,CManchester United confirm more details
OL,4,Cabout 100,000 seater stadium
OL,6,F"The publication of the Wharfside
OL,7,FMasterplan marks another significant
OL,8,Fmilestone in our journey to create a
OL,9,Fnew world-class home for Manchester
OL,10,FUnited at the heart of a vibrant and
OL,11,Ftransformational district for Trafford
OL,12,Fand Greater Manchester.
OL,14,F"Together with our partners, we have a
OL,15,Fonce-in-a-generation opportunity to
OL,16,Fdeliver a destination that creates
OL,17,Flasting benefits for supporters, local
OL,18,Fcommunities and the wider region for
OL,19,Fdecades to come.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783682373
OL,3,CManchester United confirm more details
OL,4,Cabout 100,000 seater stadium
OL,6,F"We are committed to building a world-
OL,7,Fclass stadium with our supporters, not
OL,8,Fsimply for them.
OL,10,F"Atmosphere, affordability and
OL,11,Faccessibility will remain at the heart
OL,12,Fof our plans, and we look forward to
OL,13,Fcontinuing our engagement with fans
OL,14,Fand other stakeholders as we move into
OL,15,Fthe next phase of design and
OL,16,Fdevelopment."
OL,26,@xD@MO]
