OL,3,CManchester United confirm more details
OL,4,Cabout 100,000 seater stadium
OL,6,FThe plan is expected to create
OL,7,Fimproved public transport links,
OL,8,Fenhanced rail connectivity, and
OL,9,Fextensive walking and cycling
OL,10,Finfrastructure.
OL,12,FCllr Tom Ross, Leader of Trafford
OL,13,FCouncil, said: "We are delighted to
OL,14,Fintroduce the masterplan which starts
OL,15,Fa long journey to piece together what
OL,16,Fcould happen where, to bring this
OL,17,Fworld-class cultural and sporting
OL,18,Fdestination to life.
OL,26,@uD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
