PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783682373
OL,3,CManchester United confirm more details
OL,4,Cabout 100,000 seater stadium
OL,6,F"We want to create a great place to
OL,7,Fbe, not just on matchdays but every
OL,8,Fday ` and we're looking for as many
OL,9,Fresidents and businesses as possible
OL,10,Fto help us to shape this vision,
OL,11,Fthrough our forthcoming consultation
OL,12,Fprocess.
OL,14,F48,000 local jobs and 15,000 new homes
OL,15,Fare expected to be created with the
OL,16,Fnew stadium as the catalyst.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
