OL,3,CManchester United confirm more details
OL,4,Cabout 100,000 seater stadium
OL,6,FRoss added: "Wharfside will become a
OL,7,Fnetwork of attractive neighbourhoods
OL,8,Fin which to live, work, wander,
OL,9,Fexplore, relax with family, enjoy
OL,10,Fnature and wildlife, meet friends, eat
OL,11,Fout, have a drink, shop and be
OL,12,Fentertained.
OL,14,F"It will have the best of parks and
OL,15,Fwaterside spaces, housing including
OL,16,Faffordable options in vibrant and
OL,17,Fdiverse localities, new health and
OL,18,Feducational facilities, joined up
OL,19,Fpublic transport and places to walk,
OL,20,Fcycle and be active."
OL,26,@nD@MOUvD@AOU|D@UO]
